						<p>
							This page describes how to begin a&nbsp;<b>wild Pokémon encounter</b>&nbsp;on demand. These are typically used for non-roaming&nbsp;legendary encounters, and for any other Pokémon you battle after interacting with it in the overworld (e.g. Voltorb that look like&nbsp;<a href="/web/20210512075234/https://essentialsdocs.fandom.com/wiki/Item_balls" title="Item balls">item balls</a>).
						</p>
